</tr>
<tr>
<td>S-C-05</td>
<td>Validasi - judul kosong</td>
<td>Aktifkan selection, judul kosong, submit</td>
<td>Validasi error "Judul wajib diisi"</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>S-C-06</td>
<td>Validasi - tanpa pertanyaan</td>
